cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV

The paper proposes a novel approach for efficient learning in Deep Reinforcement Learning (DRL) environments with sparse rewards, specifically in continuous DRL environments such as robotic arms control. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also mentions the use of Maximum Entropy Reinforcement Learning (MERL) and Open AI Robotic manipulation tasks, which suggest the sub-categories cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) as possible additional sub-categories.
